    <item>
      <title>大选临近，德国领导人舒尔茨支持降低食品杂货税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/german-leader-scholz-backs-lower-grocery-taxes-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨提议降低基本食品杂货的增值税，以帮助低收入家庭应对持续的高通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/german-leader-scholz-backs-lower-grocery-taxes-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会抨击英国公共薪酬提案，斯塔默面临新风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/unions-slam-uk-proposals-on-public-pay-in-fresh-risk-for-starmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国各工会组织对英国政府明年公共部门薪酬方案提出批评，这增加了英国政府采取罢工行动和制造紧张局势的可能性，并将对基尔·斯塔默政府造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/unions-slam-uk-proposals-on-public-pay-in-fresh-risk-for-starmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 22:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国召开年度经济会议讨论刺激计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-begins-annual-economic-meeting-to-hash-out-stimulus-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国定于周三召开年度经济工作会议，制定明年的政策，在与美国爆发贸易战的威胁下，高层领导人暗示将采取更有力的刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/china-begins-annual-economic-meeting-to-hash-out-stimulus-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
