    <item>
      <title>北爱尔兰支持脱欧后规则，但工会主义者抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/northern-ireland-backs-post-brexit-rules-but-unionists-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北爱尔兰议员投票决定继续执行脱欧后规则，但统一党派的反对凸显了英国政府在试图维护该地区政治稳定时面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/northern-ireland-backs-post-brexit-rules-but-unionists-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚亲欧政党承诺迅速组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/romanian-pro-european-parties-pledge-to-form-government-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚亲欧洲政党承诺迅速组建新政府，阻止极右翼掌权，并在该国最高法院宣布上一次选举结果无效后举行新的总统选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/romanian-pro-european-parties-pledge-to-form-government-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:37:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉的替身认为早已不复存在的南斯拉夫仍然是一个国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lula-s-stand-in-thinks-long-gone-yugoslavia-is-still-a-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当前的政治环境下，左翼政府的失言令人遗憾。总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦下台后，他的替补会见了一位东欧领导人，称他为三十年前苏联解体后解体的国家元首。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/lula-s-stand-in-thinks-long-gone-yugoslavia-is-still-a-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登计划阻止向新日铁出售美国钢铁业务，美国钢铁股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，一旦本月晚些时候交易被交回给拜登，拜登总统计划以国家安全为由正式阻止美国钢铁公司以 141 亿美元的价格出售给新日本制铁公司的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗里兰称加拿大将实现债务目标，但对赤字保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 表示，政府将继续实现逐步降低债务与国内生产总值比率的目标，但回避了有关预算赤字规模的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
